text: Lehel Fekete (born 31 January 1957) is a Canadian fencer. He competed in the individual foil event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Canada Category:Fencers at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ottawa
